                <li>Use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">ReadOnly</code> for scripts users should inspect but not modify.</li>
                <li>Show <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Error Text</code> with a specific count or message ("3 syntax errors").</li>
                <li>Use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">WithLineNumbers</code> whenever the editor content may be referenced by line number in error messages or logs.</li>
                <li>Toggle <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Show Status Bar=OFF</code> for ultra-compact embeds where metadata is not needed.</li>
